            <statement>
                <p>The point <m>(4,-5)</m> is on the graph in <xref ref="figure-graph-line-full">Figure</xref>. What happens when you substitute these values into the equation <m>y=-2x+3</m>?</p>
                <table>
                    <tabular>
                        <col halign="right" />
                        <col/>
                        <col/>
                        <row bottom="medium">
                            <cell><m>y</m></cell>
                            <cell><m>=</m></cell>
